    A class which provides an implementation of Cramer's rule for solving a system of equations
    CzekanovskiDiceDistance<V extends Vertex,E extends Edge<V>>
    A class for calculating Czekanovski-Dice distances With respect to Czekanovski-Dice distance, two vertices are close to each other if they have many common vertices
